# Dynamic Tariff Project Architecture

This document provides a comprehensive technical overview and visual architecture diagram of the **Dynamic Tariff** backend pricing system. The system computes hourly, next-day tariff adjustments (surges and rebates) per charger to flatten peak demand while enforcing safety and compliance constraints.

---

